navigation

Class Navigator

  • java.lang.Object
    • navigation.Navigator

  • public final class Navigator
extends java.lang.Object
    Representation of a Navigator. This (Singleton) class is responsible for properly using the WebDriver and some additional functionality.
    Author:
    Thibault Helsmoortel
